routes.documentation: List of all Recording CompositionHook resources.
Delete a Recording CompositionHook resource identified by a `CompositionHook SID`.
Returns a single CompositionHook resource identified by a CompositionHook SID.
Delete a Recording Composition resource identified by a Composition SID.
Returns a single Composition resource identified by a Composition SID.
Delete a Recording resource identified by a Recording SID.
Returns a single Recording resource identified by a Recording SID.

{
  "meta": {
    "first_page_url": "",
    "key": "",
    "next_page_url": "",
    "page": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "page_size": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "previous_page_url": "",
    "url": ""
  },
  "rooms": [
    {
      "account_sid": "",
      "audio_only": {{faker 'datatype.boolean'}},
      "date_created": "{{faker 'date.recent' 365}}",
      "date_updated": "{{faker 'date.recent' 365}}",
      "duration": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
      "empty_room_timeout": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
      "enable_turn": {{faker 'datatype.boolean'}},
      "end_time": "{{faker 'date.recent' 365}}",
      "large_room": {{faker 'datatype.boolean'}},
      "links": {},
      "max_concurrent_published_tracks": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
      "max_participant_duration": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
      "max_participants": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
      "media_region": "",
      "record_participants_on_connect": {{faker 'datatype.boolean'}},
      "sid": "",
      "status": "{{oneOf (array 'in-progress' 'completed' 'failed')}}",
      "status_callback": "",
      "status_callback_method": "{{oneOf (array 'HEAD' 'GET' 'POST' 'PATCH' 'PUT' 'DELETE')}}",
      "type": "{{oneOf (array 'go' 'peer-to-peer' 'group' 'group-small')}}",
      "unique_name": "",
      "unused_room_timeout": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
      "url": "",
      "video_codecs": [
        "{{oneOf (array 'VP8' 'H264')}}"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
responses.label: OK

routes.documentation: Returns a list of tracks associated with a given Participant. Only `currently` Published Tracks are in the list resource.
Returns a single Track resource represented by TrackName or SID.
Returns a list of Subscribe Rules for the Participant.
Update the Subscribe Rules for the Participant
Returns a list of tracks that are subscribed for the participant.
Returns a single Track resource represented by `track_sid`.  Note: This is one resource with the Video API that requires a SID, be Track Name on the subscriber side is not guaranteed to be unique.
